{"type": "article", "id": 28818, "title": "办公桌", "description": "", "date": "2016-06-29T06:59:15Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 400262, "comment_count": 4, "praise_count": 101, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160703121522CyWLD4IkENVvXjPq.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>          </p>\n<p>越来越多的办公场所采用了开放式的设计，虽然大大增加了自由度，但随之而来的却是维持注意力的问题，一些常见的干扰可能来自路过的同事或者是手边的电子设备。圣何塞州立大学的两位学生 Aaron Mazikowski 和 Sean Naderzad 设计了一款名为 Seamless 的办公桌，圆弧形的无缝结构参考了摄影棚里的白色幕布，创造出半封闭式的个人空间，阻隔了一部分视线，但又不会带给人一种被笼罩的感觉。Seamless 配置了两层木制隔板，可以放下各类办公用品。</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-active medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160703121521PBS7z3b1qUyhiWEl.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"medium-insert-image-active\" data-ratio=\"0.64714286\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"medium-insert-caption-placeholder\"></figcaption></figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160703121521Lw1ZYq3WCHOTkPuo.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.64714286\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160703121521sJG1bKpxgZH5eEkv.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.64714286\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160703121522Nvxk3uVfwR9KmgIP.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.64714286\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n\n"}